      "text": "（話し掛けてきた現地の女の子と、kanaさんが）\n（英語でペラペラ話しているが……一体何を？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That local girl who came up to us and kana-san are）\n（speaking English so fluently… What are they talking about?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと話聞いてみたんだけど\nこいつ、kanaのバズッた動画観てたんだってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I listened to her story for a bit‚ and…\nIt turns out she saw my video that went viral.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4337709169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "で、自分もインフルエンサーになりたいって言ってる\nkanaに「ヒットするコツを教えてほしい！」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And she said she wants to become an influencer too.\nShe asked kana‚ “Teach me the secrets to becoming a hit!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、だからkanaさんに話し掛けてきたんですね\n海外にもファンがいるなんて、さすがです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ so that’s why she came up to you‚ kana-san.\nYou even have fans overseas‚ as expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ま、これくらい当然だけどね\n……で、さあ。kana気付いたんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s only natural.\n…But listen. I’ve realized something…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "あのブランドで、限定バッグをサクっと買ってたし\nこいつ、多分セレブの子供だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She bought that limited edition bag from that brand without any hesitation.\nShe’s probably from a celebrity family‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ってことは、うまくおだてて親に恩を売れば\nkana達の役に立ってもらえるかもじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which means‚ if I flatter her and get on her parents’ good side‚\nthey might be able to help us out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはそうかもしれませんけど\nさすがに子供を利用するのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-That might be true‚\nbut taking advantage of a child like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "は？　kanaだってバズり方教えてやるんだから\nそれでwin-winじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? I’m going to teach her how to go viral‚\nso it’s a win-win situation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
