      "text": "『それじゃ、一緒にお茶でもしよっか\nあ、それとも、他のお店も回ってみる？』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“So‚ how about we have some tea together?\nOr should we check out some other stores?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、{user}！\n何ぼさっとしてんの、次の店行くよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}!\nWhat are you standing around for?! Let’s go to the next store!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待って下さい……\n二人分の荷物は、結構きつくてですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hold on a second…\nThis stuff for two people is pretty heavy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "ちっ、情けないなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tch‚ pathetic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.9999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.9666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "んー、でも、いい具合に目立ってる気がする\nやっぱり一人より二人、ついでにおまけ付きよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm~‚ but I think I’m getting a good amount of attention.\nHaving two people is definitely better than one‚ even with a bonus.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お二人はなんだか、さっき会ったばかりとは\n思えないくらい盛り上がってましたね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You two seem to be getting along\nreally well considering you just met…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4718229929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.7999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "まあね～。「あの男の人、kanaちゃんの\nボーイフレンドなの？」って聞かれちゃったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well yeah~. She asked me‚\n“Is that guy kana-chan’s boyfriend?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ぼ、ボーイフレンド！？\nそれで、一体なんて答えたんですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-Boyfriend?!\nSo‚ what did you tell her…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.9333323161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "あの人、kanaの大ファンだし\nkanaの言うことなんでも聞いてくれるけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He’s a huge fan of mine‚\nso he does whatever I say~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "kana、仲がいい男は他にも沢山いるから\nどうしようかなって思ってるの～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I have plenty of other guy friends‚\nso I’m wondering what to do~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.5999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "きゃ～、kanaちゃんってばさすが～！！\n……って感じかな～。きゃはっ。めっちゃ面白くない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaaa‚ kana-chan‚ you’re so cool!\n…Something like that~. Kyaha! Wasn’t it hilarious?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.3666717529
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、あいつが呼んでるから行ってくるわ\nこれ以上、遅れないでよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ she's calling me. I’ll be back.\nDon’t dawdle‚ and follow me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4299.994913799992,
          "startTime": 147.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（……英語の授業、もっと真面目に受けておくんだった）\n（せめて、訂正出来るくらいには……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…I should have paid more attention in English class.）\n（At least enough to correct her…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.9932312012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "『そうなんだ～。お父さんが社長で、うんうん』……\n――――って、それマジ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Oh‚ I see~. Your dad is the CEO‚ uh-huh.” …\n――Wait‚ seriously?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ん……何かあったのか？\nお二人とも、どうかしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Did something happen?\nIs everything alright‚ you two?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.1666798909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_02-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "いや、親はどんな人なのって、探り入れてみたんだけど\n……なんかこいつ、家出中なんだってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I was trying to pry about her parents‚\n…and it turns out she ran away from home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
